<div class="app-card-container" id="about-me-card">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img skills col-md-12' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4>React</h4>
              <h4>Ruby on Rails</h4>
              <h4>JavaScript</h4>
              <h4>Redux</h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <!-- <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div> -->
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="about-me-1">
          I'm a fullstack web developer based in New York City.
          Certified in Full-Stack Web Development at General Assembly NYC.
          I work with several lanugages and frameworks, my personal favorites are React and Ruby on Rails.
          <br><br>
          Besides Web Development work I also do Branding, SEO, Design, and Marketing.
        </p>
        <hr>
        <h5>A little more about me.</h5>
        <p class="about-me-2">
          I was born and raised in South Florida. Growing up with a passion for music I decided to pursue
          it professionally. I attended Belmont University in Nashville, TN double majoring in Music Business
          and Marketing. While in Nashville I played and toured with several different artists.
          I moved to New York City in February 2016 to pursue Web Development.
        </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              The Fragrance Group (New York, NY)
              <div class="job-title">
                Web Developer
              </div>
              <div class="job-description">
                - Designed and developed eCommerce website via Shopify.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              General Assembly (New York, NY)
              <div class="job-title">
                Fullstack Web Development
              </div>
              <div class="job-description">
                - HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Express, NodeJS, MongoDB, Ruby, React, Rails
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Belmont University (Nashville, TN)
              <div class="job-title">
                BBA in Music Business
              </div>
              <div class="job-title">
                BBA in Marketing
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
